# GenAI Flask App

A lightweight Generative AI web application built using Flask that allows users to interact with an AI model through a simple, intuitive web interface. The goal of this project is to demonstrate how Large Language Models (LLMs) can be integrated into a Python backend and served through a clean UI.

---

## Overview

This project showcases how Generative AI can be embedded into a full-stack web application using Flask. It includes a frontend powered by HTML/CSS/JavaScript and a backend API that handles user prompts, processes them through an AI model, and returns generated answers in real-time.

This repository can be used as:
- A starter template for AI web apps
- A portfolio project for demonstrating AI integration
- A learning resource for Flask beginners

---

## Features

- Interactive chat-style interface
- Flask backend with REST endpoints
- AI text generation
- Clean and minimalist UI
- Easy setup and modular codebase
- Template-based rendering (Jinja)

